WEBVTT

00:01:25.264 --> 00:01:30.704
The terror is incomprehensible
to most of us,

00:01:30.704 --> 00:01:33.159
because blindness

00:01:33.159 --> 00:01:38.829
is thought to epitomize ignorance
and unawareness,

00:01:38.829 --> 00:01:46.630
hapless exposure to the ravages
of the dark unknown.

00:01:46.630 --> 00:01:48.460
How poetic.

00:01:49.440 --> 00:01:52.801
Fortunately for me,
my parents were not poetic.

00:01:52.801 --> 00:01:54.676
They were pragmatic.

00:01:54.676 --> 00:02:01.293
They understood that ignorance and fear
were but matters of the mind,